text: "Still Got It" is a song by Tyga featuring Drake, from Tyga's album Careless World: Rise of the Last King. The song debuted at number 89 on the Billboard Hot 100 on the week ending October 29, 2011. == Charts == Charts (2011) Peak position US Billboard Hot 100 89 == References== Category:2011 songs Category:Drake (musician) songs
